Class TreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • TreeNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HuffmanNode, SplayNode

    public abstract class TreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract a binary tree node data structure superclassing both HuffmanNode and SplayNode.
